## Response Patterns

### Standard Response

```go
return response.Resp(c, response.Response{
    Data: items,
    Meta: paging,
})
```

### Success Message

```go
return response.Resp(c, response.Response{
    Messages: response.Messages{"success"},
})
```

### Custom Data

```go
return response.Resp(c, response.Response{
    Data: map[string]any{
        "paymentUrl": paymentURL,
        "orderID":    orderID,
    },
})
```

### Error Response

```go
return &fiber.Error{
    Code:    fiber.StatusBadRequest,
    Message: "درخواست شما معتبر نمی باشد.",
}
```
